# Install hblock

```sh
curl -o /tmp/hblock 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/vdbhb59/hosts/master/hblock' \
  && echo 'aeb47fce80baa1a47c907ab2b1af37de7fe68dff92fd4e7e4a5df075bf5b668f  /tmp/hblock' | shasum -c \
  && sudo mv /tmp/hblock /usr/local/bin/hblock \
  && sudo chown 0:0 /usr/local/bin/hblock \
  && sudo chmod 755 /usr/local/bin/hblock
```

# Install as SYSTEMD

Checkout the systemd document to regularly update with the current changes.

```sh
https://raw.githubusercontent.com/vdbhb59/hosts/master/systemd
```
